file.name: example4-split-openapi.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Split Public API
  description: split Public API
  termsOfService: https://split.io/legal/terms
  version: v1
externalDocs:
  description: split API documentation
  url: https://www.neoteroi.xyz/
servers:
  - url: https://www.neoteroi.xyz/split/api/v1
tags:
  - name: User
    description: Operations about users.
paths:
  /users:
    $ref: "./spec/paths/Users.yml"
  /users/{identifier}:
    $ref: "./spec/paths/UserById.yml"
components:
  schemas:
    $ref: "./spec/schemas/_index.yml"
  responses:
    $ref: "./spec/responses/_index.yml"
  parameters:
    $ref: "./spec/parameters/_index.yml"
  securitySchemes:
    ApiKeyAuth:
      type: apiKey
      in: header
      name: X-API-KEY

security:
  - ApiKeyAuth: []

Error: unmarshal: json: cannot unmarshal string into Go struct field Components.components.parameters of type ogen.Parameter
